{
  "key": 58101,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "Route210GrandmaWilmaHouse_Text_ImWilmaTeachDracoMeteor",
      "en_US": [
        "Hohoho...\n",
        "They call me Grandma Wilma.\r",
        "I came out here by myself from\n",
        "a town of Dragon Tamers.\r",
        "I can teach the strongest of all\n",
        "Dragon-type moves to the tough\f",
        "Pokémon of Sinnoh.\r",
        "Would you like me to teach that\n",
        "move to one of your Pokémon?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route210GrandmaWilmaHouse_Text_TeachDracoMeteor",
      "en_US": [
        "Ah, it is you again...\r",
        "Would you like me to teach the best\n",
        "Dragon-type move I know to one of\f",
        "your Pokémon?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route210GrandmaWilmaHouse_Text_DoComeBack",
      "en_US": [
        "Well, perhaps if you change your\n",
        "mind, do come back."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route210GrandmaWilmaHouse_Text_NoPokemonCanLearn",
      "en_US": [
        "I see...\n",
        "I like your sense of adventure.\r",
        "However, none of the Pokémon with\n",
        "you now can learn the move."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route210GrandmaWilmaHouse_Text_PickPokemonToTeach",
      "en_US": [
        "Fine, fine, now pick the Pokémon\n",
        "I should teach the move to.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route210GrandmaWilmaHouse_Text_DoesntFullyTrustYou",
      "en_US": [
        "Sorry to disappoint you...\r",
        "That Pokémon you have can learn this\n",
        "move, but it hasn’t come to trust\f",
        "you fully yet...\r",
        "Until then, I can’t make it learn\n",
        "this move."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route210GrandmaWilmaHouse_Text_CantLearnDracoMeteor",
      "en_US": [
        "Sorry to disappoint you...\n",
        "That Pokémon can’t learn this move."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route210GrandmaWilmaHouse_Text_CantTeachEgg",
      "en_US": [
        "Hmmmm...\r",
        "Teaching a move to an Egg is\n",
        "a challenge that’s beyond me."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route210GrandmaWilmaHouse_Text_AlreadyKnowsDracoMeteor",
      "en_US": [
        "Oh? That Pokémon already knows\n",
        "{STRVAR_1 6, 0, 0}."
      ]
    },
