    {
      "id": "Route210GrandmaWilmaHouse_Text_ExplainDracoMeteor",
      "en_US": [
        "Draco Meteor’s destructive power\n",
        "is awe inspiring.\r",
        "However, using it will also lower\n",
        "the Pokémon’s Special Attack."
      ]
